quran[31]{c,v,t}:
  77,20,"Di ni bɔŋɔ, Ti (Tinim’ Naawuni) bi nam ya mi ni kochɔɣiŋgu (Maniyyi bee dablim kom)"
  77,21,Ka Ti zaŋ li niŋ luɣushɛli polo din nyɛ suhudoo ni yɛmbahiga shee
  77,22,Hali ni saha shɛli Ti ni zali li
  77,23,"Ka Ti (Tinim’ Naawuni) zali Ti nam zaligu, m-bo ni ban zaandi fukumsi"
  77,24,"Dindali maa, azaaba kpeeni daa be ninvuɣu shɛba ban labsi Chiyaama ʒiri maa zuɣu"
  77,25,"Di ni bɔŋɔ, Ti (Tinim’ Naawuni) bi zaŋ tiŋgbani leei koligu"
  77,26,(Ka di laɣindi) ninvuɣu shɛba ban be bɛ nyɛvuya ni mini ban kpi (di puuni)
  77,27,"Ka Ti zaŋ zolikara niŋ di puuni, ka nyuhi ya ko’ nyɛɣisili"
  77,28,"Dindali maa, azaaba kpeeni daa be ninvuɣu shɛba ban labsi Chiyaama ʒiri maa zuɣu"
  77,29,"(Ka bɛ yɛli buɣum bihi): “Cham ya n-ti laɣim ni binshɛɣu yi ni daa labsiri ʒiri la.”"
  77,30,“Cham ya mahim shɛli din mali wula ata la shee (dina n-nyɛ ʒahannama buɣum nyɔhi).”
  77,31,"Dina m-pa mahim, di mi ku tooi taɣi ninsala ka chɛ ʒahannama buɣum zilli"
  77,32,Achiika! Di nyɛla din labri buɣum kpila din ŋmani nam yilikara
  77,33,Ka di naan ŋmani laakumi sabila
  77,34,"Dindali maa, azaaba kpeeni daa be ninvuɣu shɛba ban labsi Chiyaama ʒiri maa zuɣu"
  77,35,Ŋɔ maa nyɛla dabsi’ shɛli bɛ (niriba) ni ku tooi yɛli yɛltɔɣa
  77,36,"Bɛ mi ku saɣi ti ba, ka bɛ fabli"
  77,37,"Dindali maa, azaaba kpeeni daa be ninvuɣu shɛba ban labsi Chiyaama ʒiri maa zuɣu"
  77,38,"Ŋɔ maa nyɛla wolginsim dabsili, ka Ti (Tinim’ Naawuni) laɣim yi mini ban daŋ tooni maa"
  77,39,"Dinzuɣu, di yi niŋ ka yi mali nabiɛri shɛli, tɔ! Yin nam ya Ma"
  77,40,"Dindali maa, azaaba kpeeni daa be ninvuɣu shɛba ban labsi Chiyaama ʒiri maa zuɣu"
  77,41,Achiika! Wuntizɔriba yɛn ti bela mahim mini kobilnina puuni
  77,42,Ni binwoli shɛŋa bɛ suhi ni kuli gbaai
  77,43,(Ka bɛ yɛli ba)! “Dim ya ka nyu ka di nyɛ yolsigu n-tin ya domin yi ni daa tumdi tuun’ shɛŋa zuɣu.”
  77,44,Achiika! Lala ka Ti (Tinim’ Naawuni) yɔri ninvuɣu suma sanyoo
  77,45,"Dindali maa, azaaba kpeeni daa be ninvuɣu shɛba ban labsi Chiyaama ʒiri maa zuɣu"
  77,46,"Dim ya ka wum ya nyεɣisim biɛla, achiika! Yi nyɛla bibiɛhi"
  77,47,"Dindali maa, azaaba kpeeni daa be ninvuɣu shɛba ban labsi Chiyaama ʒiri zuɣu"
  77,48,"Yaha! Bɛ yi yɛli ba: “Kurummi ya n-ti Naawuni, bɛ bi kurinda.”"
  77,49,"Dindali maa, azaaba kpeeni daa be ninvuɣu shɛba ban labsi Chiyaama ʒiri maa zuɣu"
  77,50,Ka yɛltɔɣa dini ka bɛ (chɛfurinim’) leei yɛn ti yɛlimaŋli di (Alkur’aani) nyaaŋa